There are three licenses, one for the software library, and one for the datadata.
This product includes GeoLite2 data created by MaxMind, available from http://maxmind.com/.

If you want to avoid GeoLite2 licence, you can do so by changing the database from ip-location-db in the README to the CC0 licence data base.


